snippet.title: Cubio Brazil Alpha Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Sign up for Cubio Alpha NOW! www.playcubio.com

Prepare to create! The sandbox game creation platform where you can create, play and share with your friends! Register to have access to the Alpha and join the Cubio adventure. 

With easy-to-use tools and customizable avatars, Cubio offers a unique experience of game creation and games that inspire players and creators of all skill levels. Join the Cubio community and unleash your creativity

Follow us on our social media for more updates:
Discord: https://discord.gg/playcubio 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/playcubio 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/playcubio
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playcubio
Tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@playcubio 
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/playcubio
